text: Kytki-Yelga () is a rural locality (a village) in Nizhnebaltachevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 117 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 14 km from Nizhnebaltachevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Kytki-Yelga
